        <scopecontent id="ref10">
            <head>Scope and Content of Collection</head>
            <p>The collection contains correspondence, orders, and photographs related to American military activities in the United States and France during World War I. The collection is composed largely of personal correspondence between Loring Phillips and his parents.</p>
